<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216364>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Hapalogenys bengalensis showing chin pores and small papillae, and scaly postero-ventral part of lower (dashed arrows)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216366>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. First ventral soft rays filamentous and reaching beyond the base of first anal-fin spine." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216367>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. PAUP generated NJ tree of Hapalogenys bengalensis relationship with other species inferred from the COI sequences, Pomadasys corvinaeformis (family Haemulidae) has been used as outgroup." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216367/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

